igeo
Class IMeshType

java.lang.Object
  igeo.IMeshType

public class IMeshType
extends java.lang.Object

Visitor class to define a type of mesh to be instantiated. Used in IMeshGeo. To define custom mesh, define child class of this to override methods.

Author:
Satoru Sugihara
